                                          1318  # This static noise can be suppressed by swallowing the first `lines mod 4'
                                          1319  # partial samples after transitioning into vertical blank. This is easiest if
                                          1320  # the modulo is 0 (do nothing), 1 (reset sample when entering the last visible
